    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114410/extras/19e9caed9387a108011b04edf33c1d73.avif?t=1770365796\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《选技大乱斗》是一款免费的多人PVP策略游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融入了类Rogue和自走棋元素，带来了全新的游戏体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，玩家需要为自动战斗的英雄搭配宝物和技能，最终击败所有玩家夺得冠军。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114410/extras/92f5e6cc0e1d9370eb2ca5e9daf95073.avif?t=1770365796\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >12种流派各有特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有12个风格不同的流派，持续更新中。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机选择8个流派</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局随机出现8个流派，局局都有新体验。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种流派自由组合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同流派之间相辅相成，尝试构筑出最强组合吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114410/extras/d19c368e6fe467d4de84fce0b6146d12.avif?t=1770365796\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过百个技能，自由构筑。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60+宝物随意组合。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+英雄各具特色。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自走棋like</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八人在线，各自为战。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松上手</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切皆可随机，英雄自动战斗，解放双手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114410/extras/d500b3d9568ce446012643e22b82be89.avif?t=1770365796\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢您玩我们的游戏，希望您能在游戏中收获快乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们最早在魔兽争霸3编辑器上创造了该玩法，超过30w人游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有过万评价，总评分9.5的高分，是电子斗蛐蛐正宗原创玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们会坚持持续更新游戏，努力让游戏变得越来越好，期待大家的支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
